# ============================================================================
# KERBEROS ADMIN ACCESS CONTROL LIST (kadm5.acl)
# This file defines who can perform administrative operations on the KDC
# Format: principal_pattern permissions [target_principal_pattern]
# ============================================================================

# Grant all administrative privileges (*) to any principal ending with /admin
# This allows admin/admin@EXAMPLE.COM to manage all principals and policies
*/admin@EXAMPLE.COM    *